	<ThingDef ParentName="Celes_LegwearBase"><!--过膝袜黑-->
	<defName>Celes_KneeHighBlack</defName>
	<label>celestia black knee-high stocking</label>
	<description>A pair of black knee-high stockings that fit Celestia's figure, balancing warmth and aesthetics, often used to match a variety of outfits. \n\nBut the truth is that if it wasn't made of a stretchy material like Dust-Mech silk or synthetic fibres, it would just be a pair of slightly longer and opaque socks.</description>
